response.original_title: Norah Jones - We Love Green Festival
response.overview: Near perfect quality Pro-shot Broadcast recording of Norah Jones, recorded live at the We Love Green Festival, in Paris, France on September, 14th, 2012.  DVD has a total running time of 62 minutes, and quality is about 9/10.  Tracks are as follows:  Say Goodbye Take It Back Chasing Pirates Long Way Home Little Broken Hearts All A Dream 4 Broken Hearts Black What Am I To You? Don't Know Why Miriam Happy Pills Stuck Lonestar
response.title: Norah Jones - We Love Green Festival
